# Zero-build fallback for clangd. INACTIVE while named ".clangd.old"
# (clangd only reads a file named exactly ".clangd").
#
# Use this if you do NOT want to run `make compdb` / generate a
# compile_commands.json:  rename this file to ".clangd".
#
# Quoted local includes ("gfx.hpp" / "gfx.h") resolve relative to the source
# file automatically, so the only flag clangd is missing is where SDL3 lives.
# This path is the Homebrew (Apple Silicon) location; change it for Intel
# (/usr/local/include) or a custom prefix.
CompileFlags:
  Add: [-I/opt/homebrew/include]
